1. User management, permissions, and file system
2. Systemd, process monitoring, and log analysis
3. DNS, load balancing, subnetting, and firewalls
4. Troubleshooting network latency and packet loss

𝐂𝐥𝐨𝐮𝐝 & 𝐒𝐜𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐛𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲
5. AWS core services (EC2, S3, IAM, VPC)
6. Load balancer configurations and multi-region setups
