𝐒𝐑𝐄 & 𝐑𝐞𝐚𝐥-𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐒𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐬
19. Incident management and postmortem analysis
20. Cost optimization and performance tuning

Most engineers spend months learning fancy tools. The best ones spend that time mastering how to design, debug, and deliver under pressure.

Companies like Google, Netflix, and Amazon don’t care if you know every CLI flag - they care if you can keep systems up when things break.

